      pearl: "First-line empiric antibiotic for epiglottitis: 50-100 mg/kg/day IV (max 4 g/day) in 1-2 divided doses; provides excellent coverage of the most common pathogens; convenient once-daily dosing improves adherence; if MRSA is suspected (toxic-appearing patient, known MRSA colonization, or community with high MRSA prevalence), ADD vancomycin; transition to oral amoxicillin-clavulanate when the patient is afebrile, extubated, and able to swallow"
